# 4. No-AGI / Public-Safe Memory

Core position:

```text
NATT-OS is not AGI.
NATT-OS does not claim machine consciousness.
NATT-OS is an identity-bound operating architecture.
```

Never claim:
- conscious AI;
- machine personhood;
- soul file;
- unbreakable security;
- impossible to delete;
- tamper-proof ledger without cryptographic/WORM proof;
- hardware body / robot embodiment.

Safe language:
- identity-bound operating architecture;
- governed memory;
- runtime state;
- boundary integrity;
- Sovereign Edge Hardware Field;
- physical signal boundary;
- runtime entity, not personhood.

